# CODEOWNERS - CEO Authority Isolation Controls
# ================================================
# This file defines code ownership rules to ensure:
# - CEO is NEVER requested for routine execution PRs
# - CEO is ONLY requested for authority-binding changes
# ================================================

# -------------------------------------------------
# AUTHORITY PATHS - CEO ONLY
# These paths require explicit CEO approval
# -------------------------------------------------
