/board/         @ttony106-source
/signatures/    @ttony106-source

# -------------------------------------------------
# EXECUTION PATHS - NO CEO
# These paths should NEVER involve the CEO
# Standard automation and execution workflows
# -------------------------------------------------
# /execution/   (automation team - DO NOT add CEO)
# /validation/  (CI/CD - automated checks)
# /evidence/    (logs, hashes - automated)
# /registry/    (data updates - automated)
# /scripts/     (automation scripts - automated)

# -------------------------------------------------
# GOVERNANCE DOCUMENTATION
# Changes to governance rules require CEO review
# -------------------------------------------------
/.github/copilot-instructions.md    @ttony106-source
/.github/CODEOWNERS                 @ttony106-source

# -------------------------------------------------
# RULE: If a path is NOT listed above with CEO,
